+## Build & Deploy Reference
+
+### Build (on host)
+```bash
+cd /root/chromium/src
+autoninja -C out/ArmQnx content_shell
+```
+
+### Package
+```bash
+cd /root/chromium/src
+./build_scripts/package-content-shell.sh
+```
+
+### Deploy
+```bash
